*****:Eclipse Shortcuts:*****

upper case: ctrl + shift + x

lower case: ctrl + shift + y

printline: syso + ctrl + space

main method: main + ctrl + space

loops and conditions: for/while/if/if else/switch + ctrl + space

move statements: place the cursor on the line and alt + up arrow  or alt + down arrow

place the code in loops/conditions/trycatch blocks : highlight code and alt + shift + z

getters and setters and constructor: alt + shift + s

correct indentaion format: ctrl + shift + f

single line comment: ctrl + /

multi line comment: ctrl +shift + /

import package: ctrl + shift + o

change the name globally: alt + shift + r

delete the line: ctrl + d

paranthesis begining and ending: ctrl + shift + p

font size: ctrl + shift + "+" or ctrl + shift + "-"
